## One more important check

Make sure the redirect URI in all three places is exactly the same:

1. In Keycloak client config
2. In `appConfig.getRedirectUri()` from Lancelot
3. In token request via `tx.getRedirectUri()`

It must be exactly:

```text
https://arthur-core.kubernetes.localhost/arthur-core/auth/callback
```

No trailing slash differences, no `/callback` vs `/auth/callback`, no internal cluster URL.

