## Best next version of `handleCallback`

Refactor the top of it like this:

```java
public void handleCallback(String code, String state) {
    AuthTransaction tx = redisAuthTransactionService.findByState(state);
    if (tx == null) {
        throw new IllegalStateException("Invalid or expired state");
    }

    AppConfigResponse appConfig = lancelotClient.getApp(tx.getAppId());
    validateAppConfig(appConfig);

    String redirectUri = tx.getRedirectUri();
    String codeVerifier = tx.getCodeVerifier();

    if (redirectUri == null || redirectUri.isBlank()) {
        throw new IllegalStateException("Missing redirectUri in auth transaction");
    }
    if (codeVerifier == null || codeVerifier.isBlank()) {
        throw new IllegalStateException("Missing codeVerifier in auth transaction");
    }

    OidcMetadata metadata = oidcDiscoveryClient.loadMetadata(appConfig.getIssuerUri());
    String tokenUrl = metadata.getTokenEndpoint();

    log.info("Callback state={}", state);
    log.info("TX appId={}", tx.getAppId());
    log.info("TX redirectUri={}", redirectUri);
    log.info("TX codeVerifier present={}", true);
    log.info("TokenUrl={}", tokenUrl);

    Map<String, Object> response = webClient.post()
            .uri(tokenUrl)
            .contentType(MediaType.APPLICATION_FORM_URLENCODED)
            .body(BodyInserters.fromFormData("grant_type", "authorization_code")
                    .with("client_id", appConfig.getClientId())
                    .with("client_secret", appConfig.getClientSecret())
                    .with("code", code)
                    .with("redirect_uri", redirectUri)
                    .with("code_verifier", codeVerifier))
            .retrieve()
            .onStatus(HttpStatusCode::isError, clientResponse ->
                    clientResponse.bodyToMono(String.class).flatMap(body -> {
                        log.error("Token endpoint error body: {}", body);
                        return Mono.error(new IllegalStateException("Token exchange failed: " + body));
                    }))
            .bodyToMono(new ParameterizedTypeReference<Map<String, Object>>() {})
            .block();

    log.info("Token exchange succeeded");
}
```

